    Interface FilterOperators<TValue>

    A type that extends Document but forbids anything that "looks like" an object id.

    interface FilterOperators<TValue> {
        __id?: never;
        $all?: readonly any[];
        $bitsAllClear?: BitwiseFilter;
        $bitsAllSet?: BitwiseFilter;
        $bitsAnyClear?: BitwiseFilter;
        $bitsAnySet?: BitwiseFilter;
        $elemMatch?: mongodb.Document;
        $eq?: TValue;
        $exists?: boolean;
        $expr?: Record<string, any>;
        $geoIntersects?: { $geometry: mongodb.Document };
        $geoWithin?: mongodb.Document;
        $gt?: TValue;
        $gte?: TValue;
        $in?: readonly TValue[];
        $jsonSchema?: Record<string, any>;
        $lt?: TValue;
        $lte?: TValue;
        $maxDistance?: number;
        $mod?: TValue extends number ? [number, number] : never;
        $ne?: TValue;
        $near?: mongodb.Document;
        $nearSphere?: mongodb.Document;
        $nin?: readonly TValue[];
        $not?: TValue extends string
            ? RegExp
            | FilterOperators<TValue<TValue>>
            : FilterOperators<TValue>;
        $options?: TValue extends string ? string : never;
        $rand?: Record<string, never>;
        $regex?: TValue extends string
            ? string
            | RegExp
            | mongodb.BSONRegExp
            : never;
        $size?: TValue extends readonly any[] ? number : never;
        $type?:
            | "string"
            | "symbol"
            | "undefined"
            | "object"
            | "double"
            | "array"
            | "binData"
            | "objectId"
            | "bool"
            | "date"
            | "null"
            | "regex"
            | "dbPointer"
            | "javascript"
            | "javascriptWithScope"
            | "int"
            | "timestamp"
            | "long"
            | "decimal"
            | "minKey"
            | "maxKey"
            | mongodb.BSONType;
        id?: never;
        toHexString?: never;
        [key: string]: any;
    }
